data.description: Nestled under large beautiful Magnolia & Oak trees awaits your new home! With a little TLC, this could be your dream home. Property offers two bedrooms with an office and two bathrooms. The seller has already taken care of two major expenses- a roof replacement in Dec 2018 and re-piping completed in 2020. Relax and enjoy your coffee while you sit in the Florida room. The backyard is fenced and private with lots of space to park your boat or RV. St. Augustine South is a nice quiet neighborhood that's centrally located with two boat ramps and no HOA fees! Just minutes from shopping & restaurants. Take a walk along the scenic shore Dr and enjoy the breeze and view of the intracoastal.
